{
  "stem": "19807.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 91.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were in the underground and we were part of the Hagana.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then when we had our kibbutz in the desert, we were all under the command of the Palmach, which was the elite force of the Hagana.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we were part of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we trained with them and we grew up with them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of our main things in that time was to guard the water pipe that they had put from Nir Am down to all the settlements so we can get water.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the Arabs enjoyed blowing it up at times, so we-- our-- one of the main duty was to watch over that water pipe.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And of course, there were other duties after that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And during the war, we left Geva.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We established [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And it was-- it was a tough time.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I would say there was another miracle.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If you can think about those days in Israel, there were only 600,000 Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And when the War of Independence broke out and Ben-Gurion announced that we are a state now and we were all related and we're in the kibbutz and all of a sudden, we were attacked by all these Arab armies.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we were in an outpost there that we were sent to guard it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the British-- I mean the-- the Egyptians were passing through with their armor.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They could have overrun us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And our settlement was bombed by the-- by the Egyptians.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they were on top of a hill which is called Tell el'Farah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "But it was a very minor one and luckily we did not get any-- any serious damages to our kibbutz.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
